a.n: Desire Passion: The Black Corset Odyssey Part 3

p.k: When her unfaithful husband (Luke Hotrod) starts bringing models home for "after-hours work", Chantel (Anny Aurora) doesn't think her heart can sink any lower. But her friends, Nina (Luna Corazon) and Jade (Rina Ellis) know exactly how to cheer a girl up!
